ISLAMABAD, Apr 4 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif on Tuesday expressed grief over the death of the brother of former federal minister Moula Bux Chandio.
In a condolence message, the prime minister prayed for the departed soul to rest in peace and for the grant of courage to the bereaved family.
